                    <div class="row">

                    <div class="col-md-12">

                  <p>  The Sugar Association of London is the trade association for the international raw sugar trade and The Refined Sugar Association is the trade association for the international white refined sugar trade.   Each Association is entirely separate with a different Membership and managed by a separate Council.</p>

                    </div>

                    </div>

