											</div>

											

										</div>

										<div class="row">

											<div class="col-md-12" align="left">

                                             <p>&nbsp;</p>

												<p>Since 1882 The Sugar Association of London  has been providing its Members with Rules And Regulations providing contract  terms for the international raw sugar trade and high quality arbitration  service for dispute resolution.</p>

                                                <p>This website provides information about  the SAL Council, Panel of Arbitrators, Members and becoming a Member.   It also provides the current Rules And Regulations  setting out the contract terms in the Contract Rules and our current Arbitration  Rules.   Also available are our past Contract  Rules providing contract terms.</p>

                                            </div>

                                         </div>

