											<div class="col-md-12" align="left">

                                             <p>&nbsp;</p>

                                            <p>The Refined Sugar Association was founded  in 1891 and it too provides its Members with Rules And Regulations providing  contract terms for the international white refined sugar trade and high quality  arbitration service for dispute resolution.</p>

                                                <p>This website provides information about  the RSA Council, Panel of Arbitrators, Members and becoming a Member.   It also provides the current Rules And  Regulations setting out the contract terms in the Contract Rules and our  current Arbitration Rules.   Also  available are our past Contract Rules providing contract terms.</p>

